HashInsight Complete Mining Platform
Complete Platform Package v2.1.0

This package contains the complete HashInsight Mining Platform with all three core modules:
1. Mining Core Module - Mining analytics and performance monitoring
2. Web3 Integration Module - Blockchain integration and smart contracts  
3. User Management Module - User authentication, CRM, and billing

